INSERT INTO `recipes` VALUES (61,3,'Standard Weapons','','#C16------------------------------\n#C12Information#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nSome standard weapons can be built. In order to know how, just go to a Generals Store and buy a manual which is sold in Weapon Recipes Shop.\n\nIngredients can be found in Weapon Construction Shops or Weapon Components Shops. Now you just have to follow manual''s instructions.\n\nThe process is long because you have to find all ingredients, of nearly QL.\n\nHere is a #L "List of Manuals" "/tell <myname> rshow 69" for Standard Weapons.\n');
INSERT INTO `recipes` VALUES (62,1,'Jewels','','#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\na Ring or Bracer\n(ie:#L "Engagement Ring" "136603")\n<img src=rdb://84061>\n\n#L "Generic Ring Template" "151365"\n<img src=rdb://84063>\n\n#L "Personal Furnace" "150930"\n<img src=rdb://149949>\n\n#L "Precious Metal Reclaimer" "150929"\n<img src=rdb://149942>\n\n#L "Wire Drawing Machine" "150917"\n<img src=rdb://149952>\n\nAnd, if you want to crimp it :\n#L "Perfectly Cut Gem" "151552" #L "Recipe" "/tell <myname> rshow 117"\n<img src=rdb://136593>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nPrecious Metal Reclaimer\n#C15+#C20\na Ring or Bracer\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://151012>\nan Ingot\n(ie:#L "Small Gold Ingot" "151369")\n#C16Skills: |  ME  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nPersonal Furnace\n#C15+#C20\nan Ingot\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://149950>\nLiquid Metal\n(ie:#L "Liquid Gold" "151372")\n#C16Skills: |  ME  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nWire Drawing Machine\n#C15+#C20\nLiquid Metal\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://151015>\nMetal Wire\n(ie:#L "Gold Filigree Wire" "151368")\n#C16Skills: |  ME  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nGeneric Ring Template\n#C15+#C20\nMetal Wire\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://151923>\nPrecious Metal Filigree Ring\n(ie:#L "Gold Filigree Ring" "151375")\n#C16Skills: |  ME  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nFrom this point, two paths are possible... either sell this ring or crimp it with a Valuable Stone to make it even more valuable. to crimp it, follow this recipe:\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nPerfectly Cut Stone\n#C15+#C20\nPrecious Metal Filigree Ring\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://84061>\nCrimped Ring\n(ie:#L "Gold Filigree Ring set with a Perfectly Cut Gem" "151541")\n#C16Skills: |  ME  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Comments#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nConsidering the time involved in the matching of QLs and the actual crafting, it''s not really worth it for me. But if you have some Mechanical Engineering Skill, it may still be interesting...\n\nMaking Jewels with SL stones will give you some little buff according to this :\n    \n<highlight>Almandine<end> - Strength / Agility  \n<highlight>Amber<end> - Melee init / Psychic Init / Ranged Init  \n<highlight>Aquamarine<end> - SensoryImp. / Psycho Mod / MaxHealth  \n<highlight>Balas Ruby<end> - AddAllOff  \n<highlight>Black Opal<end> - AddAllDef  \n<highlight>Chrysoberyl<end> - Max Health / Heal Delta  \n<highlight>Coral<end> - Nano Delta / Heal Delta / Max health  \n<highlight>Demantoid<end> - MeleeDamageMod / ProjectileDamageM / EnergyDamageMod  \n<highlight>Diamond<end> - SpaceTime / PshychoMod  \n<highlight>Emerald<end> - BiologicalMet. / SensoryImprov.  \n<highlight>Fire Opal<end> - FireAc / MaxHealth  \n<highlight>Jet<end> - MaterialMet. / NanoC.Init  \n<highlight>Pearl<end> - ChemicalAC / ColdDamageMod.  \n<highlight>Red Beryl<end> - Stamina / Intelligence  \n<highlight>Ruby Pearl<end> - Sense / Intelligence  \n<highlight>Sapphire<end> - MaterialMet. / BiologicalMet / MaxNcu  \n<highlight>Star Ruby<end> - MaterialCreation / SpaceTime / MaxNanoEnergy  \n<highlight>Topaz<end> - EnergyAC / ProjectileAC  \n<highlight>Water Opal<end> - NanoDelta / MaxNanoEnergy  \n<highlight>White Opal<end> - ColdAC / PoisonAC\n');
