INSERT INTO `recipes` VALUES (71,1000,'Instructions for the good old recipes of Mother Bea','','#C12 Ingredients #C20\n    Before each recipes, a list of ingredients is given. To know where you can find theses, just click on the link on the bottom of the recipe''s window.\n    \n#C12 Recipes #C20\n    Everywhere in this Book, you''ll find the Recipes explained under this form :\n    \n    | SK | #C16 [Item 1] + [Item 2] = [Item 3] #C20\n    Here this recipe means : Pick Item 1 and make Shift+Right Click on Item 2 to get Item 3. Remind that in this recipe, Item 1 and Item 2 are lost during the process. This manipulation require some skill in "SK".\n    \n    Or\n    \n    | SK | #C16 [Item 1]#C12 * #C16  + [Item 2] = [Item 3] #C20\n    Now this recipe means : Pick Item 1 et make Shift+Right Click on Item 2 to get Item 3. Same as before but the Item 1 (the tool, in fact) is not lost during the process. As before, this manipulation require some skill in "SK".\n    \n#C12 Shortcuts of Skills #C20\n    - CL : Computer Literacy\n    - NP : Nano Programming\n    - ME : Mech Engi*\n    - EE : Elec Engi*\n    - QT : Quantum FT*\n    - WS : Weapon Smt*\n    - PT : Pharma Tech*\n    - CH : Chemistry\n    - BE : Break and Entry\n    - PS : Psychology\n\n    The Skills noted with * can be buffed for 125pts by the Traders.');
