INSERT INTO `recipes` VALUES (105,3,'Sealed Weapon Receptacles','','#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nA Sealed Weapon Receptacle\n(ie : #L "Sealed Weapon Receptacle - Alsaqri Chemical Rifle" "157670"\n<img src=rdb://157448>\n\n#L "Hacker Tool" "87814"\n<img src=rdb://99282>\n\n<highlight>The Missing Part...<end>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nThe first thing to do is to pry open the Sealed receptacle to get the unfinished weapon.\n\nHacker Tool\n#C15+#C20\nSealed Weapon Receptacle\n#C15=#C20\nUnfinished Weapon\n#C16Skills: |  BE  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nNext, you must apply to the Unfinished Weapon the required missing Part. Here is the list of all theses parts:\n\n<img src=rdb://13312>\n#L "Unfinished Alsaqri Chemical Rifle" "157668"\n#C15+#C20\n<img src=rdb://130741>\n#L "Self-Repairing Ultra-X" "137284"\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://13312>\n#L "Alsaqri Chemical Rifle" "157661"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Unfinished HSR Explorer 661" "157674"\n#C15+#C20\n<img src=rdb://130693>\n#L "Generic Magnetic Propulsion System" "137246"\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "HSR Explorer 661" "157666"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n<img src=rdb://13313>\n#L "Unfinished IMI Tellus TT" "157646"\n#C15+#C20\n<img src=rdb://130787>\n#L "Flake Tubing Super-Coolant System" "137250"\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://13313>\n#L "IMI Tellus TT" "157628"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n<img src=rdb://113989>\n#L "Unfinished Ithaca Ki12 Vulture" "162907"\n#C15+#C20\n<img src=rdb://130746>\n#L "Nano-Interfaced Cooling System" "137270"\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://113989>\n#L "Ithaca Ki12 Vulture" "162902"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n