INSERT INTO `recipes` VALUES (575,6,'The Special Hidden Recipe of Leet''s Slippers','','#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\ntwo leets\n<img src=rdb://156598>\n<img src=rdb://156598>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nfirst of all, you have to catch 2 leets. It`s easy, make a trap using a box, a wooden twig, a wire and a bronto burger. after somes time of hunting you will have your two leets.\n\nNext you have to turn over the leet, that process consist in making sure the fur of the leet is inside. Easiest way to do this is simply to put your hand in the leet, but it''s needed to get inside him from the rear.\n\nTo finish, grab the teeths of the leet and pull on them,  you have to pull in a quick movement in order to turn over the leet as a sock.\n\nDo the same with the next leet. here it is ! you go a perfect Leet`s slippers ! hot, soft, ... that`s wonderful\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Comments#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nWhen your Leet`s slippers becaume cold, you can put them some seconds in the microwave.\n\nAfter 5 times in the microwave, build another one. due to smelling purpose...\n');
