INSERT INTO `recipes` VALUES (583,5,'Drake Trial''s Quest','','#C16------------------------------\n#C12Quest Info#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nFind Drake Rodriguez in Jobe Backyard. ( You have to be below level 50 to enter job backyard ). Drake will give you 5 little quests and\n\na #L "Bracer of Jobe" "223762".\n<img src=rdb://227249>\n\n<highlight>Test of Strength<end>\n\nYou have to kill a Deceitful Weaver, a Shining Coiler and a Beit Gras in 30 minutes. You can do that easily at around level 3.\n\nReward: #L "Bracer of Strength" "223771" \n<img src=rdb://84047>\n\n<highlight>Test of Agility and Stamina<end>\n\nYou have to target a Hungry Predator, a Lurking Chimera and a Pond Dryad in 3 minutes !!! so be quick.\n\nReward : depending on you profession.\n\n<highlight>Test of Sense<end>\n\nDrake ask you to find a shadowleet. you can find him by using the search icon on menu 2 ( CTRL+2) near the guards area.\n\nReward: #L "Nano Crystal (Overview of Nascence)" "223768"    \n<img src=rdb://12259>\n\n<highlight>Test of Psychic<end>\n\nTalk to Talk to Celeth-El (omni) or El-Domo(clan) and complete his quest\n\nReward: #L "Ring of Enhanced Psychic" "223769"    \n<img src=rdb://84059>\n\n<highlight>Test of Intelligence<end>\n\nYou have to deliver some supplies to Sarah Willis. Sarah Willis is behind a big creature you can''t kill, so you have to distract it. For that, speak to Brad Willis ( a mixture between Brad pit and Bruce Willis ... ) he will fight the creature while you speak to Sarah. then return to Drake.\n\n<img src=rdb://205499>\nReward: #L "Bonfire Kit" "223773"\n    \n<highlight>Final Test<end>\n\nFind Heckler of Evolution, kill him and loot the\n\n#L "Delicate Metal Device" "223763"\n<img src=rdb://227248>\n\nfrom him. Go back to Drake and trade him the device.\n\nReward: #L "Smart Backpack" "223770"\n<img src=rdb://99661>\n');
